o work with me, and has asked me for some money for certain of his relatives in Florence. I am sending this money to thee: go, therefore, immediately to Bonifazio and he will give thee four broad ducats, which thou art to give to Meo di Chimenti, the stonecutter, now working for the Cathedral. Give him the letter enclosed in this and addressed to him. Let him give thee a receipt signed with his own hand to the effect that he has received this money from me on behalf of Michele. Send on the receipt to me.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"077b0750-32ed-4325-a6ac-18fb7af00b27","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":9,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"46ea397e-c5bd-49be-95ef-b8fed4f98ae5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":9,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"54c54da6-c2d1-4bfc-86fe-9e6186827683","type":"codex/trait-reference","start":18,"end":28,"value":"913ca4c1-eef5-40b2-84f8-e9cfae49c603","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"47368744-c5ac-4234-9acb-1878e2605837","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":30,"end":36,"value":"b6faa55d-91eb-4e79-9140-c053bcda079f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2b84a7b8-6341-4651-8897-1dfed5beb8ca","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":47,"end":50,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7e402d39-deb0-4b43-b01e-164ea3c8ff9b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":65,"end":66,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d0e73fb9-64b7-43ca-befc-1f35e09874fd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":83,"end":84,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"cda4b163-406e-484d-9d84-5abd289bfcf5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":116,"end":118,"value":"b6faa55d-91eb-4e79-9140-c053bcda079f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6ef84066-9e1c-4cf1-b777-b319d514e350","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":133,"end":